There was a loud screech as Trelos forced open the door to his CR
open.  It was opening under its own power, but he was far too
impatient for that.  The door, now detached from its hinges, was
thrown six meters from the chamber against the wall impacting the wall
before falling to rest on the floor and causing enough noise that it
could be heard throughout the base.

He stepped out of the chamber, for a moment forgetting his
surroundings.  He was overcome with a surge of energon for a brief
moment, then returned to a normal defensive posture, realizing he was
not in a jail cell.

